Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.87,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Love lasts forever, riddles are puzzling...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.87,0:00:28.37,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}...and Saturday nights are for mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:30.76,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yūsaku Kudō's creation, the Night Baron,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:32.92,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}has entered the real world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:34.62,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:36.46,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the brain of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.46,0:00:38.31,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:22.00,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Night Baron
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.65,0:00:03.46,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The Night Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.46,0:00:08.35,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}My dad, Yūsaku Kudō, wrote a novel about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:10.88,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A phantom thief maneuvering in the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:14.08,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and a ruthless killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.08,0:00:17.48,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today, let's play back the case where this mysterious person
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:22.00,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}broke free from the novel and appeared in the real world!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:31.67,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,Izu Princess Hotel - Private Beach
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:37.47,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirō Kon'no (28)\NBank Employee
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:51.82,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokio Ebara (32)\NComputer Programmer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:59.25,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen'ichirō Kaneshiro (74)\NComputer Company Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:04.17,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizue Hayashi (56)\NKaneshiro's Butler
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:03.16,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru Maeda (30)\NJōnan University Electrical Engineering Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.83,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideko Kamijō (29)\NSoftware Company CEO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:39.71,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko Sayama (24) -\NHigh School Math Teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:19.41,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,Agasa Residence
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.18,0:19:56.84,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,Observation Lounge
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:54.97,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Hotel 2F Pub Emerald
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:28.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I hate this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:31.58,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Why am I in such a hot place
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:34.43,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}at such a hot time of the year?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:39.81,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This is all because of\Nthe doc's phone call...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:41.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Izu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:45.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Three days and two\Nnights at a hotel in Izu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And for free, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:50.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:52.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Free sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:55.99,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What am I doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:03:02.19,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I should be out looking for\Nthose men in black who shrunk me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:10.95,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But the occasional break is nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:14.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?\NYou should come swim, too, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:16.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.31,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Eh, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:25.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only half has been paid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:29.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. A reservation for three in the name of Agasa, right? There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:32.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible! Check again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:39.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you! Only half of\Nthe hotel's cost has been paid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:42.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with paying half then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:45.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't bring that\Nmuch money with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:48.37,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Come to think of it, the doc {\i1}did{\i} say...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:50.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it {\i1}really{\i} free?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:53.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In your case, Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, it's as good as free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:55.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In my case? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:56.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:04:02.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My scientist friends and I like\Nto communicate via PC lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:06.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them found an interesting\Ntour on an online forum
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:10.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and invited me to apply for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:13.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called the 'Izu Mystery Tour'.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:14.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystery tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:20.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, my friend, his granddaughter,\Nand I all were chosen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:25.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But his granddaughter caught a cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:28.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so now I'm offering you our spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:32.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Six parties will attend -\Nten people in all, including you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:34.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone gets a 50% hotel discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:38.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the tour organiser is one\Nof the other seven people,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:41.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and whoever figures out who\Nthat is gets to stay for free
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:46.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and wins floppy disks\Ncontaining a certain program.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:49.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though you wouldn't have a use for the program...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:53.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So how do I look for this\Nmysterious organiser?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:55.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:59.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We received the names and room\Nnumbers of all the attendees.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:02.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the organiser's supposed\Nto play a certain character
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:06.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and cause an incident during the tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:07.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain character?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:12.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a character you know\Nvery well from novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:13.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:15.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Night Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:18.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're him, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:25.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,3.04 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:30.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how long you took\Nto respond to my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This was most informative.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:35.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shirō Kon'no, Room 2002.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.97,0:05:38.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:42.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never find the Baron's identity that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:48.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who\Nanswered in 2.86 seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:49.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0030,,Ebara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Room 2101.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:52.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0030,,Do you ever shut up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:56.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0040,,Exposing oneself when caught off-guard
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:59.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0040,,{\i1}is{\i} the way of man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:01.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0035,,Isn't that right, Shizue{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:04.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0035,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:07.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaneshiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Room 2001...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:11.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It took you 6.29 seconds to respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:13.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes are bad, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:18.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected you\Nwould question me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:22.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. I'll know the\Ntruth once I process this data.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:24.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that data's incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:29.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still missing\Nsomeone's information.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:32.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0020,,Isn't that right, Mr. Night Baron?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:36.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-what was that,\NKamijō{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} of Room 2102?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,0.97 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:44.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Add it in after my\N1.48 seconds, Kon'no{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:44.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:45.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:48.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this Baron thingy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you don't know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:53.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.\NHe's just playin' innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:57.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he shows up in lots of\NShin'ichi's dad's novels!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:59.43,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:05.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The Night Baron is an elusive\Nvillain created by my father, Yūsaku Kudō!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:13.25,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He's a thief of the darkness\Nand sometimes a crazed murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:18.67,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}My father, Yūsaku, hasn't revealed\Nthe Night Baron's identity yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:25.75,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}but either way, whoever's using his\Nname is one these people...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:29.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This makes no sense.\NI'm going to our room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:33.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! What about the money for the hotel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:39.14,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hold on. There were\Nsupposed to be ten people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:43.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}With me, Ran, the old man and the other five, we're just eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:44.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We're missing two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:50.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it's just your butt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:54.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don'tcha come with me and fill my drinks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:55.78,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:01.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0030,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:03.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0030,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:06.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Satoru Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:08.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-{\i1}néechan{\i}. Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:14.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Know? He was Japan's karate champ six years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:17.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the reason I started\Npracticing karate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:23.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ran Mouri! I won\Nthe recent city championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:27.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A karate champ and a city champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:31.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected to meet\Nyou here! I'm super-lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:33.15,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Who's super-lucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:34.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:36.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:37.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0030,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:39.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0030,,This is my fiancée, Akiko Sayama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:42.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting married?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:44.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:49.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take it personally.\NAkiko gets jealous pretty easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Night Baron, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:56.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Room 1901, Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}... 0.75 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:09:00.43,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He's still at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:05.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's strange. You're supposed to be\Ntwo doctors and a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:10.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They couldn't come,\Nso we came in their place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:14.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my father, and he's\Na detective, not a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:18.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:21.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. His name is Kogorō Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:24.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kogorō Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:26.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen him in the newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:29.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they say he's a great detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:33.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How dirty of him to send\Na detective instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:36.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come now. We have\Nfewer possible Barons now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:43.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But with Kogorō Mouri here,\Nwe cannot afford to show our faults.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:46.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like Dad's famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:49.45,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}All thanks to me, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:53.87,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Who's there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:57.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:00.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to our room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:05.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, {\i1}that's{\i} the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:09.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why they were shocked\Nwhen I said Dad was a detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:13.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's basically like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:18.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I find which of those\Nseven is the Night Baron,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:21.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we get to enjoy\Nthe Izu Beach for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:26.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's why Dr. Agasa told Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} it was free!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:28.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:33.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course! Because there's no mystery that I, Kogorō Mouri, can't solve!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:35.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:40.03,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}You were just ranting about going\Nhome 'cause you have no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:45.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! I better go do\Nmy preliminary questioning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:48.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's in such high spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:50.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we look around the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:52.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:55.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?\NLet's move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:58.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stay here\Na little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:11:02.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Well, I'll be in the\Ngift shop downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll be there in a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:06.89,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:11.19,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Why were they all so shocked\Nat the mention of a detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:13.06,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's just a game, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:16.57,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}All you get is to stay\Nfor free, so why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:19.91,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And that murderous glare!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:23.11,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And then there's what\Nthe doc said...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:27.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...and wins floppy disks\Ncontaining a certain program.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:31.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though you wouldn't have a use for the program...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:33.34,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.26,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I've got a bad feeling about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:44.48,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Guess I can just call him after\Ndinner and get all the details...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.90,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The Night Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.57,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The Night Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.58,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:22.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:23.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Damn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.45,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:47.57,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He must've changed in the toilet\Nand then taken the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:50.29,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But who dressed up as\Nthe Night Baron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:55.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Without counting me, Ran or the old man, there's seven people on this tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:13:01.92,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The purpose of the tour is to find\Nits organiser among the attendees.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:07.68,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The organiser who would cause\Nan incident as the Night Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:11.52,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But it's just a simple\Ngame to stay for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:16.43,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Who'd push someone off\Njust for {\i1}that{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:19.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that program?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:21.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:28.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea. All the ad said was that\Nit was the "ultimate program."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:33.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that reminds me.\NMy doctor friend mentioned
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:36.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,something or other about a virus...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:38.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A virus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:43.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's odd, though. He shouldn't\Nknow any more about it than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:46.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, doc! Don't tell me that virus is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:49.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-{\i1}néechan{\i}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:55.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?! I've been waiting\Nat the gift shop this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?! You're dripping wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:05.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I, uh, slipped and fell into the pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:10.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nothing to laugh about!\NWhat's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:15.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't seem hurt.\NGo change and then we'll have dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:23.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:25.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:28.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:32.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! And Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Sayama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you three doing together?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:38.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father just finished\Ninterrogating us...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:42.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"You're the Night Baron, aren't you?!" and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:47.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! That's a lovely dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:50.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:56.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But be careful. Some perverted wolf might be on the prowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:01.97,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That old perv just doesn't learn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:06.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} signed you up\Nfor this mystery tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:10.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Akiko's a huge fan\Nof Yūsaku Kudō's novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:14.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the Night Baron ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:18.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody knows more about\Nthe Night Baron than I!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:21.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my hairstyle\Nis the same as his!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:27.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the only expert\Non the Night Baron...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:30.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:35.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that's food for thought.\NNow if you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:40.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What an outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:43.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's{\i} why Mom ran out on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:45.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit ogling her, Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:49.17,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That {\i1}is{\i0} one great outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:51.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:55.34,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Huh? The old perv didn't\Neven glance at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:57.90,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Maybe she's not his type?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:04.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's Kaneshiro{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}, Room 2001...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:07.02,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Looks like Shizue Hayashi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} isn't with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:09.94,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Okay! Time to do some investigating!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:11.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:14.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:17.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! You've had too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:22.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, mister, are you after the\Ncomputer virus too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:26.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Conan Edogawa from Room 1902.\NDo you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:31.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From whom did you hear about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:36.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The people on the tour keep\Ntalking about a virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:39.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know why\Nthey're talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:42.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All they should know is that\Nit's the "ultimate program..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:45.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:48.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was once a mysterious\Ncomputer virus that infected
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:53.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,computers at large corporations\Nand ravaged all the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.73,0:16:59.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, it is an unstoppable\Nand undetectable "perfect program."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:05.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, it was so elusive\Nthat the people named it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:06.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Night Baron!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:09.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Night Baron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:13.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who knows\Ncomputers knows its name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:17.97,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I see. And the tour organiser\Nis also named the Night Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:21.93,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So that gives some idea as to\Nthe contents of the program!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:24.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing that name\Nbrings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:29.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of my son who\Ndied four years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.27,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Son?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:33.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing! Bye, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:43.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Shizue{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.\NThat lad is one sharp rascal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:45.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:50.46,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's Kon'no{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} from Room 2002.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:51.92,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Looks like he's on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:54.51,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wonder what he's talking about{\i}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:59.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it {\i1}was{\i} Tokio Ebara...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:02.26,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Tokio Ebara? The old perv?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:06.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So he was the hacker?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:11.19,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A hacker?! A person who\Nsteals computer data?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:14.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:21.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want one of these someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch Satomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:27.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:30.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the name of my mother\Nwho died last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:32.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Satomi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:36.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:40.01,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This guy's named his PC\Nafter his dead mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:43.63,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh? The old perv's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:47.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Miss! Do you know where the person who was sitting here went?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:49.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He went back to his room\Nto do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:55.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy, if you know him,\Ncould you return this to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:19:00.03,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Come to think of it, he had this necktie wrapped around his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:01.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:02.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Ran-{\i1}néechan{\i}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:08.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you "Ah, Ran-{\i1}néechan{\i0}" me! Always sneaking around like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:09.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.99,0:19:14.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} all went to their rooms long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:18.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Looks like Dad's not back yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:20.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Akiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:22.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me in already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:24.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah right, you flirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:27.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you've had\Ntoo much to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:29.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:33.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She says I was eyeing the waitress...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:34.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:41.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll go up to the top\Nlounge until she cools off...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:44.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come too, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:49.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:51.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.47,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The starry sky looks so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:03.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but not nearly as pretty as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:06.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just teasing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:11.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, the ocean's pitch black.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:14.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oceans sure are creepy at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:20.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, when did you first meet Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:25.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid. I was best\Nfriends with her older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:28.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He died three years ago, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:31.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s brother passed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:34.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Sounds like everyone else here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:39.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-{\i1}neéchan{\i}. Where did Uncle go anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:41.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him earlier with a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:45.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijō{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} from Room 2102, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:46.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:49.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Forgot about the {\i1}other{\i0} old pervert...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:52.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0040,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:55.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0040,,I see, so you were married...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:58.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I divorced three years ago, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:01.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would anyone divorce\Nsuch a beautiful woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:05.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, could you tell me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:08.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know who the Night\NBaron is by now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:13.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you! The hotel fee's at stake here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:19.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on! At least a hint!\NPlease, Mr. Great Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:22.68,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}She's got great boobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:28.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:32.44,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This could be one fun night!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:39.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, guess I should\Nget back to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:41.77,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yeah, get lost already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:44.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko should have cooled off by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:48.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus I'd get bitten if\NI stay with you any longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:51.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...by your little bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:53.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:57.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, do you know what the virus is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.96,0:22:00.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Virus? Like a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:03.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevermind...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.75,0:22:06.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of weird question was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:15.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:18.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:19.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.21,0:24:04.21,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A person wearing a mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.21,0:24:07.96,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So it {\i1}was{\i0} the Night Baron who fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.30,0:24:12.56,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.93,0:24:17.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A security lock on the inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:20.11,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Which means this is a locked-room murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:26.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The Night Baron!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.35,0:24:27.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.96,0:24:32.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Night Baron Murder Case (Suspicion Part)"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.39,0:24:37.38,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Next Conan's Hint: Security lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.38,0:24:39.41,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10\an8}Oh, that's a drama series that's getting popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.41,0:24:42.76,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10\an8}No, that's "bolt lock."
